# NEXT_PUBLIC_* are inlined into the browser bundle at build time.
# Cloud Build cannot see .env.local (gitignored + dockerignored), so these
# public values must live in a file the build stage actually reads.
# These keys are public by design — Supabase anon key is shipped to every
# browser; treating it as a secret offers nothing.

